property.name: displayText
property.value: To fight enemies you need to get close to them to hit them with your [RED]mighty battle axe! [BLACK]But if you come close to enemies they will also try to hit you. So try to defend yourself with your [RED]shield. [BLACK]To use the shield press the [BLUE]right mouse button [BLACK]or the [BLUE]controller button A.

property.name: displayText
property.value: After fighthing an enemy your HP and Shield might be lowered. To recharge them use health or shield items. There might be some in this cheest. Open it using the [BLUE] E key [BLACK] or the [BLUE]controller button Y.

property.name: displayText
property.value: Dwarfs are known to be [RED]mighty wariors[BLACK] and the [RED]greatest blacksmithes in all nine worlds[BLACK]. But not as gread swimmers. So stay away from water.

property.name: displayText
property.value: Some enemies are stronger than others. They can take more damage and deal more damage to you. They also behave different. But all of them have one thing in common. [RED] They can be killed!

property.name: displayText
property.value: To get rid of bats the [RED] spin attack[BLACK] is very usefull. To activate it, push and hold down the [BLUE]left mouse button[BLACK] or the [BLUE]controller button B, till you hear a sound that indicates that the attack is charged. Then release the attack button and use the spin attack to [RED]crush your enemies!

property.name: displayText
property.value: You can run faster for some time by pushing the [BLUE]shift key[BLACK] or by [BLUE] pushing down the analog stick of the controller[BLACK]. But that will cost endurance. If you have no endurance left you can not run faster anymore and can not attack for some time.

property.name: displayText
property.value: Arrows can be used to attack distant enemies. To use arrows they have to be chosen in the pause menu. Use the [BLUE]escape key [BLACK]or the [BLUE]controller button 'start' [BLACK] to open the menu. They can be shot using the [BLUE]space key [BLACK] or the [BLUE]controller button X[BLACK].
